<br>
It appears all Inny worshipers are KoS, along with Iksars, and quite possibly many other evil types. I've been trying to raise my faction without hosing my Katta faction, and here is what I've found:<br>
<br>
There are 7 Seru factions that I know of - <br>
Hand of Seru<br>
Eye of Seru<br>
Heart of Seru<br>
Shoulders of Seru<br>
Seru<br>
Citizens of Seru<br>
Hand Legionaires<br>
<br>
I've found that the names of the mobs are VERY misleading as to what faction they are on, so do NOT trust the mob name. For example, the mobs in Marus Seru, named &quot;A Hand of Seru&quot; which con dubious to me, appear to be on Hand Legionaires faction (first hit on the list when killed). The mobs in Dawnshroud Peak, which I believed are named &quot;Legionaire XXX&quot; I'm going to assume are on the same faction (will kill one to verify). However the mobs inside Sanctus Seru, aslo named &quot;Legionaire XXX&quot; appear to be on Hand of Seru faction (again first hit when killed).<br>
<br>
So, apply a little logic (which isn't 100% foolproof either), it would appear that the faction needed to clear the first set of guards is &quot;Hand of Seru&quot;. This faction can be raised by either killing Recursos in Marus Sactu (very green at 60, druid and paladin class mobs) or by killing Spire Sprites in Mons Letalis (a bit harder, some are light blue, Necros, and the zone is much more dangerous, however you get Citizen's faction with these and not with the recursos). <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showMessage?topicID=9405.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showMessage?topicID=9167.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8875.topic&index=46><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.emailToFriend?topicID=8875.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.threadControl?topicID=8875.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8875.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8875.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email 